reviewText: Not working on my DVD.msg. Said to check the DVD if there's a scratch.need to return it

If you have been following the events as they unfold, the episodes contained in this volume are as must have to watch all over again.  The main event is the farewell send off that the Lim family prepares and presents to Maya as she goes on to see her dream of becoming a Flight Attendant come true.  If you are buying just specific volumes, this is the must have volume.
